<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <title>Contact Us</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="CSS/Contact_Us.css">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="IMG/spirals.png">
</head>
<body>
<div class="head-bar">
    <%- include('./layout/NavBar') %>
</div>
<div class="header2">
    <h1>
        Contact Us
        <br>
        <span style="font-size: 25px">Let us help you explore what you love</span>
    </h1>
</div>

<div class="container">
    <div class="Contact LeftContact">
        <p>We appreciate your interest in our historical monument destination and are here to assist you with any
            inquiries or feedback you may have.</p>
        <p>
            We also value your feedback and suggestions so please feel free to reach out to us using the contact details
            provided below.
        </p>
        <p class="text">
            <i class="fa fa-map-marker"></i> Số 8A Tôn Thất Thuyết, Mỹ Đình, Nam Từ Liêm<br>
            <i class="fa fa-map-marker"></i> Hà Nội, Việt Nam<br>
            <i class="fa fa-phone-square"></i> <a href="tel:0123456789">02432321284</a><br>
            <i class="fa fa-envelope"></i> <a href="mailto:nhattruong5114@gmail.com">nhattruong5114@gmail.com</a>
        </p>
        <div class="map">
            <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d8481.902586661165!2d105.78030173056202!3d21.02908408821946!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x3135ab86cece9ac1%3A0xa9bc04e04602dd85!2zRlBUIEFwdGVjaCBIw6AgTuG7mWkgLSBI4buHIFRo4buRbmcgxJDDoG8gVOG6oW8gTOG6rXAgVHLDrG5oIFZpw6puIFF14buRYyBU4bq_IChTaW5jZSAxOTk5KQ!5e0!3m2!1svi!2s!4v1688212310420!5m2!1svi!2s"
                    width="100%" height="100%" style="border:0;" allowfullscreen="" loading="lazy"
                    referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"></iframe>
        </div>

    </div>
    <div class="Contact RightContact">
        <p>
            You can also use the contact form on this page to send us a message directly. We strive to
            respond to all inquiries promptly and provide you with the assistance you require.
        </p>
        <div>
            <p>Please provide your contact information as well as your questions or feedback, we will get back to
                you as soon as possible.</p>
        </div>
        <form id="contact-form" action="">
            <div>
                <label for="full-name">Full Name <span style="color: red">*</span></label>
                <div>
                    <input type="text" id="full-name">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div>
                <label for="email">Email Address <span style="color: red">*</span></label>
                <div>
                    <input type="email" id="email" required>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div>
                <label for="phone">Phone Number</label>
                <div>
                    <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" placeholder="Ex: (123)-456-789">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div>
                <label for="subj">Choose Subject</label>
                <br>
                <select id="subj" name="subject" required form="contact-form" style="width: 100%">
                    <option value="General_Enquiry">General Enquiry</option>
                    <option value="FeedBack">Feedback</option>
                    <option value="Other">Other</option>
                </select>
            </div>
            <div>
                <label for="msg">Message <span style="color: red">*</span></label>
                <div>
                    <textarea id="msg" placeholder="Messages or feedbacks here."></textarea>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <input id="submitBTN" type="submit">
                </div>
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="footer">
    <%- include('./layout/footer') %>
</div>
<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.0/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>